{"tid":1476804,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［風向撚］發唔發覺有人刻意杯葛不撐警集會 想滅聲","createTime":"2019-08-16T02:38:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T03:28:45.000Z","uid":217816,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5956e5cd28fccf48b2742fc74a51fd0095942543","tid":1476804,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"我講緊呢單野堆回覆<br />\n「警員親屬連線」計劃舉辦「還警於民」集會遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1476549\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1476549</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n首先黑警無個係好人/黑警應該死全家大家都知<br />\n知還知<br />\n但如果呢個社會上有人出黎要求成立獨立委員會查黑警<br />\n其實都係我地五大訴求之一<br />\n佢地仲要suppose係對面啲人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以佢地出聲更加幫到我地突顯警察濫權既問題<br />\n係不論派別都不能容忍既</span></span><br />\n就好似公務員果日出黎集會咁<br />\n係更加有力既聲音<br />\n點解單單因為人地身份問題要叫人收皮 <br />\n用仇恨既口吻黎排斥佢地？<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家係想幫黑警手 叫佢地唔好出黎？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係咪有人想帶風向<br />\n排斥一切反警察既集會？嘗試滅聲</span></span><br />\n請槍口對外<br />\n訴求同路既集會，就算身份唔同，就算我地唔參與，<br />\n都唔好排斥/矮化/叫人收皮<br />\n唔係既，你同幫黑警叫「不撐警集會」收皮有咩分別？？"},{"pid":"3696e131204a31e67f3e1fdea6bf246a6d3e76f1","tid":1476804,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf10c75a9e7cf5c69e3eb74666240afc0bb8070a","tid":1476804,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c762285cd6fd37a30e86c15f31001cc8963f4ece","tid":1476804,"uid":217816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaecde729ad0e3ce03b8dc807ce4eb43f23428